  "texts": [
    "The network with a higher AUC score typically has better capabilities in distinguishing between fake and real instances.",
    "In addition, the Wilcoxon rank sum test is also performed based on the Fig. 8 ROC curves for Celeb-DFv2 using EfficientNet-B0 models with manual and optimal hyperparameters identified by all search methods scores (see the last columns in Tables 10, 11 and 12), which are all lower than 0.05 for all three test sets.",
    "This indicates that our optimized EfficientNet-B0 models outperform those devised by other search methods with a statistical significance.",
    "The mean optimized hyperparameters over 5 runs for EfficientNet-B0 using the sampled combined dataset are provided in Table 13.",
    "These yielded hyperparameters by different search methods are analysed to justify performance variations in the optimized networks."
